name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.datanode.lazywriter.interval.sec
description: Interval in seconds for Datanodes for lazy persist writes.

name: dfs.datanode.ec.reconstruction.stripedread.timeout.millis
description: Datanode striped read timeout in milliseconds.

name: ipc.client.idlethreshold
description:
Defines the threshold number of connections after which
               connections will be inspected for idleness.

name: dfs.image.parallel.threads
description:
The number of threads to use when dfs.image.parallel.load is
        enabled. This setting should be less than
        dfs.image.parallel.target.sections. The optimal number of
        threads will depend on the hardware and environment.

name: dfs.namenode.lease-hard-limit-sec
description: Determines the namenode automatic lease recovery interval in seconds.

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.am.job.task.listener.thread-count
description:
The number of threads used to handle RPC calls in the
    MR AppMaster from remote tasks

name: dfs.namenode.maintenance.replication.min
description: Minimal live block replication in existence of maintenance mode.

name: file.bytes-per-checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  file.stream-buffer-size
